name: Back in Time For a Dime

description:
Thanks to overwhelming fan support, everyone's favorite redhead is back! After some bumps in the road, it seems MJ is finally over Spider-Man and excited to go to Homecoming with her boyfriend, Harry Osborn. But unless Harry's dad sees an improvement in his son's slipping grades, Harry can forget about ever seeing Mary Jane again. Add to this the fact that Liz Allen thinks best friend MJ and boyfriend Flash Thompson are fooling around behind her back, and you've got a recipe for the worst Homecoming ever! Pick up the newest installment in Marvel's most mischievous melodrama, and discover why Entertainment Weekly featured this electric teen drama in its Must List! Collects MARY JANE: HOMECOMING #1-4.

Story Titles

  • The Cheating Thing
  • The Friendship Thing
  • The Regret Thing
  • The Homecoming Thing
name: Homecoming

description: This comic contains reprints of several Batman stories from the 1930s and 1940s.
name: Batman

description: A story that aims to explore the very essence of the cyberpunk tradition: Nathan, Sigmund and a cyber-cowboy named Case (but not "that" Case...)  must get deep into the cyberspace to track down some dangerous viruses that have attacked research centers and databases.
name: Cacciatori di virus

description: A strange outbreak seems to lead to suicide several cybernauts . A hacker named Igor McNally asks for help from Nathan , who discovers a strange plot that also involves the myth of Prometheus .
name: Istinto Primordiale

description: The Alpha Agency carries out on behalf of the military a complicated and dangerous investigation about the  beautiful Rebecca Taylor , a memory carrier that cannot anymore download  files stored in her mind.
name: Blocco mentale

description: A seemingly ordinary mission for Nathan and Legs: to help a famous writer of action novels, Ella Richards, to retrieve his identity, lost between dreams and memories that no longer seem to belong to her. In reality, what seems to be a psychoanalysis subject proves to be a powerful esper, whose HIP (High Induction Power, or hypnotic induction quotient), inherited from the mother, ties her unconsciously in the life of her twin sister, Nikki. Behind this, the shadow of the military Intelligence ...
name: Il sogno della farfalla

description: Since this first " Summer annual " , Martin Mystere and Java makes the acquaintance of Angie , the airhead stripper who will co-star almost all the Speciale Martin Mystère issues.  In this adventure , Martin Java and Angie engage in researching , in the heart of the Indian jungle , the legendary Gold en Cobra , and meet a holy man with extraordinary powers that leads them to an incredible mystery of extraterrestrial origin .
name: Il Cobra d'Oro

description: Martin Mystère , Java and Angie are in Scotland to investigate one of the classic mysteries of all time : the monster of Loch Ness . But others are in the game: the archenemy Sergej Orloff and the two louts Dee and Kelly , self-styled descendants of the sixteenth century occultist John Dee and Edward Kelly , at their first appearance here . Together they will discover the amazing , true nature of the legendary Nessie .
name: Il tesoro di Loch Ness

description: The fate of some men , inexplicably identical to each other in every way , intersects with that of Detective of the Impossible who, along with Java and Angie , must go to Egypt . The solution of the mystery lies behind the Pyramids of Giza , and is linked to the remote history of the lost continent of Atlantis .
name: Il segreto della grande piramide
The trail of the pharaoh's eye
